import React from 'react' import { Button, Row, Col, Table, ListGroup, Image, Card} from 'react-bootstrap' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' import { useDispatch, useSelector } from 'react-redux' import Message from '../components/Message' import FormContainer from '../components/FormContainer' import CheckoutSteps from '../components/CheckoutSteps' function PlaceorderScreen() { const cart = useSelector(state => state.cart) cart.itemsPrice = cart.cartItems.reduce((acc, item) => acc + item.price * item.qty, 0) cart.shippingPrice = cart.itemsPrice > 100 ? 0 : 10 cart.taxPrice = Number((0.15 * cart.itemsPrice).toFixed(2)) cart.totalPrice = (Number(cart.itemsPrice) + Number(cart.shippingPrice) + Number(cart.taxPrice)).toFixed(2) const placeOrder = (e) => { console.log('Order') } return ( <>
